{"id": 1935, "genre": 1001, "title": "你通过游戏获得过哪些新知？", "description": "游戏领进门，修行在个人。 （题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 2520, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170929114147YHDinjcZdRS1wOMC.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-10-04T17:00:28Z", "options": [{"id": 240128, "content": "你之所以赢是因为电脑想让你赢。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147452}, {"id": 240129, "content": "团队协作也是在整个团队能力差不多的情况下发挥的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146850}, {"id": 240385, "content": "人名币玩家～", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 886966}, {"id": 240130, "content": "玩上古卷轴让我深刻了解到MOD的重要性。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 185428}, {"id": 240386, "content": "认真你就输了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102915}, {"id": 240131, "content": "钟爱推箱子，发现逻辑思维真的很巧妙", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118037}, {"id": 240132, "content": "经验很重要！要学会分析！在适当的时候一定要花钱！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147463}, {"id": 240388, "content": "没有最好的，只有最合适的。\n并不是平平整整的才是最合适的，有时需要起起伏伏(高高低低)才能度过难关。\n尽管再好的东西一直给你，没有打好好的基础，你也会处理不来。\n除了后一步，还要考虑未来，不要为了当初的将就，而导致未来的一发不可收拾。\n还有强迫症不要玩这个游戏\n——俄罗斯方块\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148377}, {"id": 240133, "content": "风暴暖暖让我见识了暴雪审美", "image": "img/option/option/20171005094241EzHTuRDkoA46Oi0g.jpg", "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 985797}, {"id": 240389, "content": "一大错觉…你能反杀……该跑的还是得跑的…", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1145108}, {"id": 240134, "content": "三国志11，背下了三国地图。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147468}, {"id": 240390, "content": "玄学是欧洲谎言", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148391}, {"id": 240135, "content": "玩cytus、deemo后反应速度明显提高，妈妈再也不用担心我掉手机了，空中一手捞。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 583966}, {"id": 240391, "content": "团队合作非常重要", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148387}, {"id": 240137, "content": "玩《三国志》记住中国地形和三国重大时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147481}, {"id": 240138, "content": "我不仅是个学渣，玩游戏好像也没什么天赋", "image": null, "praise_count": 228, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 837558}, {"id": 240394, "content": "CSGO玩家，英语口语水平极大提高。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525930}, {"id": 240139, "content": "天下武功唯快不破", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1085613}, {"id": 240140, "content": "俺们90后应该是与腾讯网游接触的最多了吧，马哥让我明白 玩游戏 得充值", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960649}, {"id": 243980, "content": "猥琐发育", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164958}, {"id": 240141, "content": "一段历史故事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981357}, {"id": 240397, "content": "王者  让我知道了人多力量大   团啊！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148410}, {"id": 243981, "content": "才能成功", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1164958}, {"id": 240142, "content": "小时候玩大富翁让我有一种买股票就能发家致富的错觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131493}, {"id": 240398, "content": "我命由我不由天。承君此诺，必守一生。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617528}, {"id": 241166, "content": "全世界各大航线，历史古迹，人文地理", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1103238}, {"id": 240143, "content": "从谐克莽、莽克狗、狗克偷、偷克稳、稳克谐中领悟了经济学消费与投资的艺术、博弈论、以及人生哲学。", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069515}, {"id": 240144, "content": "比如AK47", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 782955}, {"id": 240146, "content": "王者让我明白了趁年轻要努力发展自己，不要急于求成，猥琐发育，，，", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1146323}, {"id": 240147, "content": "刺客信条啊，维多利亚事情的著名人物啊和法国大革命呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900957}, {"id": 240148, "content": "只是来看如何自己骗自己...", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819615}, {"id": 240150, "content": "自从玩了欧陆风云，觉也不睡了，饭也不吃了，西方哪个国家都去过了，动不动就喊一句，大明天下无敌啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133557}, {"id": 240151, "content": "玩三国杀了解了很多三国人物吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147279}, {"id": 240152, "content": "玩守望先锋知道了用各国语言怎么说你好==", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147279}, {"id": 240153, "content": "记得要团啊～", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 832119}, {"id": 240410, "content": "与！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147244}, {"id": 240155, "content": "啥也没学到，就是玩玩", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 240411, "content": "兽人永不为奴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148020}, {"id": 240156, "content": "实况足球让我爱上足球", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672996}, {"id": 240412, "content": "再牛逼的游戏，也有过不去的坎???", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 712861}, {"id": 240413, "content": "奶妈死哪去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1096805}, {"id": 240414, "content": "要积极尝试，善于接受未知事物，不要故步自封。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1148458}, {"id": 240415, "content": "剑侠情缘", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 494480}, {"id": 240160, "content": "ssr没有六星暴击御魂重要。。。再多的ssr没有御魂也是N", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 240416, "content": "一个人走得快，一群人走得远-求生之路", "image": "img/option/option/20171006193425drXTxRgF1L27BsUb", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112601}, {"id": 240929, "content": "约炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 916733}, {"id": 240162, "content": "《正常的大冒险》改变了我的罗辑思维。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1142637}, {"id": 238883, "content": "不知道有多少男生的三国人物和时间线都是因为《三国志》而牢记的，反正我是", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 240163, "content": "不一样的爱情——沙耶之歌\n玄不济非，氪不改命——崩坏3\n你再牛队友不行还是输——王者荣耀\n原来游戏还可以这么做——Icey", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1118633}, {"id": 240675, "content": "搞不搞一个人完全取决于他技能交了没有;-)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1073756}]}